name: FAGS
description:
I love fags as much as the next man, and what better way to celebrate this than with a pack of Ultra Horse endorsed pack of delicious fags?

NB No actual fags are inside. Instead there's 3 mini zines:
France - and the people in it.
Kittens of 2010 - an overview.
Animals  of Farthing Wood - Fox Fights back. He's not taking any more of your bullshit.

All of extraordinary high quality. 
The size of a normal pack of 20 smokes, the colour of a normal tube of aquafresh toothpaste, how can you go wrong? 

Currently featured in Berlin's Wunder kabinet exhibition as part of Etsy Labs. That's right folks, these babies are internationally renowned. Checkit http://thewunderkabinet.wordpress.com/2011/06/01/no-3-aka-the-reading-raum/

name: E.T Cereal mini zine box
description:
That's right folks it's another Ultra Horse mini zine spectacular, this time in the form of the killer E.T cereal packet housing THREE mini zines all with various 'How-to' by E.T themes, all in glorious techni-colour!
Contains:
"E.T and the Art of Love" - Learn to woo that broad!
"E.T cooks with Nutella" - Learn some culinary skills with your fave chocolate spread
"E.T Arts and Crafts" - Learn to make a felt mouse, and other stories.

All the mini zines are cut and pasted onto pages of old 'Jackie' magazines, so if you're lucky you may be able to read a bit of Cathy and Clare problem page in the background too. Bonus!
The boxes themselves are made from recycled high quality hymn books.

name: I Like Going To The Cinema - A Decade by Damn England
description:
I like going to the cinema.
I've collected every stub/memory from all movies I've seen.
I've put them together in this zine.
It tells a story.  It's funny.  It's honest.
You will have seen some of these movies too and maybe you'll remember some shit too.

A zine by Damn England - Editor of Constipated Rhythms

name: Constipated Rhythms - Issue 4
description:
A genre defining statement of intent!
After a 3 year break Constipated Rhythms erupted back onto the zine scene with this frankly, outright rude zine.

Full of your favourite swear words and plotless comic strips!
Laugh!
Then discard!

name: Constipated Rhythms Issue 5
description:
